CustomField.description: List of object API names separated by ";" whose email attachments and files need to be exported to Amazon S3. If "All", all email attachments will be moved to Amazon S3. If empty, no email attachments will be moved to Amazon S3.
CustomField.inlineHelpText: List of object API names separated by ";" whose email attachments and files need to be exported to Amazon S3. If "All", all email attachments will be moved to Amazon S3. If empty, no email attachments will be moved to Amazon S3.
CustomField.label: Objects to Export Email Attachments
